  "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nPrysm takes up more and more memory until it stops. Why?\r\n\r\nThis is my startup command\r\n\r\n```\r\n./prysm.sh beacon-chain --slasher --execution-endpoint=http://127.0.0.1:8551 --jwt-secret=/root/prysm/jwt.hex --chain-id=1 --datadir ='/home/www/eth_data' --mainnet --checkpoint-sync-url=https://sync.invis.tools --genesis-beacon-api-url=https://sync.invis.tools -- enable-experimental-state --p2p-max-peers=20 --grpc-max-msg-size=1000000000\r\n```\r\n\r\ngeth version geth version 1.13.2-stable-dc34fe82\r\n\r\nLatest Prysm version is v4.1.1.\r\n\r\nRun using screen\r\n\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/assets/128539227/e98a7e5f-db40-44c1-b6eb-ab5348f5e545)\r\n![image](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/assets/128539227/369a51f1-a8aa-4ea4-b779-3c4fbcf9ae93)\r\n\r\n\r\nThis will eventually happen\r\n![image](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/assets/128539227/038e06cd-4b5f-4d4a-9487-79cf98cd51a1)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Has this worked before in a previous version?\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### 🔬 Minimal Reproduction\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Error\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Platform(s)\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### What version of Prysm are you running? (Which release)\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Anything else relevant (validator index / public key)?\r\n\r\n_No response_",
